snippet.title: Quantum Rush Champions - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Released in 2014, GameArt Studio brought us their attempt at a modern wipEout clone to Steam with Quantum Rush Champions. Well, the game does have mixed user reviews on Steam, but at least it's far, FAR better than Ampersand.

Quantum Rush Champions (C) GameArt Studio GmbH
Steam page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/317440/Quantum_Rush_Champions/
